column8: Aviation has come a long way in the past 100 years, with probably the most influential component being the Jet engine. Taking aircraft higher, faster and smoother than propellor's, the jet engine really has had an impact on the industry. I am glad I was born during, not before the "jet age" and have created this design to admire it! I have used a cross-section of a jet with some of the more notable events of the jet-age positioned around it.
column21: Aviation has come a long way in the past 100 years, with probably the most influential component being the Jet engine.Show it your admiration with this t shirt from weadmire.net.
